1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:18,720
Welcome to this introductory practice.

2
00:00:18,720 --> 00:00:28,920
Please find yourself a suitable and comfortable location.

3
00:00:28,920 --> 00:00:46,520
It is better if the light is not too bright at this moment.

4
00:00:46,520 --> 00:01:05,520
See if your location is safe and secure from any disturbance.

5
00:01:05,520 --> 00:01:17,600
Keep your back straight.

6
00:01:17,600 --> 00:01:25,720
Realize yourself with your surroundings.

7
00:01:25,720 --> 00:01:43,520
Identify your precise location exactly where you are.

8
00:01:43,520 --> 00:02:00,320
Be gentle with yourself and kindly accept whatever feelings emerge during this practice.

9
00:02:00,320 --> 00:02:22,400
Channel love in your own direction using your mind, your heart and the energy of your total being.

10
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:40,960
Be kind to this body that you are about to observe.

11
00:02:40,960 --> 00:03:10,920
Allow your eyes to relax and rest your gaze downward at a 45 degree angle approximately.

12
00:03:10,920 --> 00:03:34,840
So that your eyes are relaxed.

13
00:03:34,840 --> 00:04:04,760
Find a spot where your eyes can stabilize their gaze.

14
00:04:04,760 --> 00:04:34,680
The purpose of this practice is to stabilize yourself presence and your mind while keeping the eyes open.

15
00:04:34,680 --> 00:05:04,600
And resting peacefully in this safe and comfortable location.

16
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:34,600
Without concentrating on the single spot.

17
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:50,520
Allow your eyes to peacefully and passively gaze downward.

18
00:05:50,520 --> 00:06:20,440
Without applying any strong focus, simply passively observe downward and start sensing your breathing.

19
00:06:20,520 --> 00:06:43,480
Your attention gently moves towards the breathing observation.

20
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:58,440
Allow your eyes to passively gaze downward.

21
00:06:58,440 --> 00:07:19,400
While you are beginning to observe your breathing body.

22
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:28,360
Observe your breathing process.

23
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:49,320
When thoughts arise, shift your mind towards the breathing process.

24
00:07:49,800 --> 00:08:12,280
Allow your eyes to continue resting peacefully and observing downward without any concentration.

25
00:08:12,280 --> 00:08:29,240
A passive gaze.

26
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:46,200
While you are observing your breathing body.

27
00:08:46,200 --> 00:09:03,160
Observe how your body is breathing.

28
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:32,120
You are peacefully observing your breathing.

29
00:09:32,120 --> 00:10:01,080
If you wish to close your eyes, you may do so and you may also keep them open.

30
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:17,080
Observe your breathing body.

31
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:57,080
In you to observe the breathing body.

32
00:10:57,240 --> 00:11:12,040
Notice how the body is breathing.

33
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:27,000
Notice any sensations arising in your body.

34
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:51,960
Without reacting, continue the observation of your breathing body.

35
00:11:57,960 --> 00:12:11,960
With eyes opened in a relaxed fashion.

36
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:26,920
With eyes closed, you continue to simply observe the breathing body.

37
00:12:42,920 --> 00:13:06,920
You may hear the sounds around you if any.

38
00:13:06,920 --> 00:13:27,880
While you are peacefully resting in your location.

39
00:13:27,880 --> 00:13:52,840
Your eyes are not engaging with anything.

40
00:13:52,840 --> 00:14:17,800
You may notice how the body is breathing by itself.

41
00:14:18,520 --> 00:14:42,760
You are just a spectator of this peaceful process.

42
00:14:42,760 --> 00:14:59,720
Observer of how the body is breathing by itself.

43
00:14:59,720 --> 00:15:10,680
How everything is happening by itself.

44
00:15:11,160 --> 00:15:19,640
And you are just simply present.

45
00:15:20,120 --> 00:15:32,600
Without doing anything.

46
00:15:32,600 --> 00:15:45,560
Presence.

47
00:15:45,560 --> 00:16:10,520
Witness the natural breathing of the body.

48
00:16:15,560 --> 00:16:40,520
Relax and witness this moment.

49
00:16:45,560 --> 00:17:10,520
You are relaxed and peaceful.

50
00:17:10,520 --> 00:17:35,480
Observer of your breathing body.

51
00:17:35,480 --> 00:18:00,440
Of this moment.

52
00:18:05,480 --> 00:18:20,440
This body.

53
00:18:20,440 --> 00:18:31,400
This moment.

54
00:18:50,440 --> 00:19:01,400
Thank you.

